title: 15: What it's like Partying with TikTokers in LA
description: Just last weekend Sadie booked a last minute trip to Los Angeles with her best friend Rilyn. Both of them having 0 clue of what to expect little did they know this would be a weekend they’d never foget. Experiencing the party scene in LA, meeting the OG tiktokers, Sadies new crush, and how she almost f*cked a dilf are just a few topics explained in todays episode. Listen in to hear it all :)
